description:
Philips AquaTouch shaver 3000 gives you a convenient and comfortable wet or dry shave. With 5D Pivot & Flex heads, ComfortCut blade system, and 60 minutes of shaving, this shaver can handle all your grooming needs. 

Product Features:

Get a comfortable dry or refreshing wet shave with Aquatec
5D Pivot & Flex Heads follow curves for a comfortable shave
60 minutes of cordless shaving after a 1 hour charge
Pop-up trimmer for moustache and sideburn trimming
Skin Protection System allows smooth gliding to protect skin
name: Philips Shaver Series 3000 Wet And Dry With Pop Up Trimmer 1EA
